# Docket project

Personal job application tracker for Baseer. Standalone: own DB, own auth, own deployment.

- Domains: `baseer.humza-butt.space` / `baseer-staging.humza-butt.space`
- API: `baseer-api.humza-butt.space` / `baseer-api-staging.humza-butt.space`
- Single-level CNAMEs only (free Universal SSL)
- npm workspaces + Turborepo only — never pnpm/yarn
- Free Cloudflare tier: no Containers, Queues, or Advanced Certificate Manager
- Canonical agent docs: `AGENTS.md`. Sync rules with `npm run rules:sync`.
